{"id":108,"name":"Al-Kawthar","nameArabic":"الكوثر","transliteration":"Al-Kawthar","type":"meccan","ayahCount":3,"verses":[{"n":1,"text":"إِنَّآ أَعۡطَيۡنَٰكَ ٱلۡكَوۡثَرَ","translit":"Inna aAAtaynaka alkawthara","translation":"Indeed, We have granted you, [O Muhammad], al-Kawthar"},{"n":2,"text":"فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَٱنۡحَرۡ","translit":"Fasalli lirabbika wainhar","translation":"So pray to your Lord and sacrifice [to Him alone]"},{"n":3,"text":"إِنَّ شَانِئَكَ هُوَ ٱلۡأَبۡتَرُ","translit":"Inna shaniaka huwa alabtaru","translation":"Indeed, your enemy is the one cut off"}]}